hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"55cbaf83-ec18-4147-8950-585e0c4aaba7\">Multiple Partial Refund</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"957d2006-c589-4751-a1a0-174321a498e2\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3795b679-c38a-4fae-88f4-7a3498c5b08e\">Refund Validity (days)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f5634ea-ac19-47ae-9a88-b4b2d4a3d107\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d1760170-fa28-4c8b-b533-419100be3192\">Compatible integration</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"60823a34-d1b1-427e-90ab-60a877255f19\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">Payment flow</h2><ul data-block-id=\"87e150ea-d71b-4e40-805e-37f955bc4810\"><li data-block-id=\"181c2d2a-6bc1-4209-a3fb-e13e8dd48e77\"><p data-block-id=\"078e1e91-d284-47a0-a29a-426ce92c9228\">Dekstop QR Flow</p><p data-block-id=\"2d2d0c92-9a2a-44f4-b24d-8935f1b5c147\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6a83948a-6dd9-4373-acc8-1ec7ac527112\"><p data-block-id=\"f80c34a6-7003-4f04-b4bc-b55ce4f84da4\">Redirection</p><p data-block-id=\"ab746d61-9884-4a77-9707-3c45e7466808\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d48ec69a-d382-4ca9-8b77-c05727a2fafe\"><p data-block-id=\"39e9bdca-ba9b-4df1-8360-90ba1e6bc862\">Deeplink (H5)</p><p data-block-id=\"32f3df61-ab83-4f4c-bc2a-111ababeda16\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li><li data-block-id=\"63fd7739-70c9-438d-b0d2-3a7d79310203\"><p data-block-id=\"3d009435-05e1-4dd0-8e3d-8c38c7e5ca76\">Push Notification</p><p data-block-id=\"3defe89e-0791-4760-80ef-6058d12d4775\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"7cacbff0-6097-4577-8bea-2670eefceb05\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"3a86b5ec-38da-4400-83d2-ef1024cbe6c9\"></p><p data-block-id=\"12295416-ce37-4b1f-ae9c-e422707d5254\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"PSBank Online Banking","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"PSBank Online Banking","Slug":"psbank-online-banking","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"68d9a823-fa5d-4e84-81c5-b391f8bc0243\"><img data-block-id=\"8cd42fa4-6e06-4866-a4cd-856f0d96ab36\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/PSbank_logo.svg.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"199\" height=\"69\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" style=\"width:199px;height:69px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"b0dcfe8a-7ef5-4a82-af23-5787faf15452\">Philippine National Bank (PNB) adalah salah satu lembaga keuangan tertua dan paling tepercaya di negara ini. Untuk mengikuti kebutuhan perbankan modern, PNB menawarkan <strong>PNB Internet Banking</strong> dan <strong>PNB Digital App</strong> untuk menyediakan cara yang nyaman, aman, dan efisien bagi nasabah untuk mengelola keuangan mereka. Platform-platform ini memungkinkan pengguna untuk melakukan berbagai transaksi, mulai dari transfer dana dan pembayaran tagihan hingga pemantauan akun dan isi ulang prabayar.</p><p data-block-id=\"457f5b81-f1f9-4cd0-851c-de7d224547dd\">PNB Online Banking dirancang untuk perorangan dan bisnis, memudahkan penanganan transaksi keuangan kapan saja, di mana saja. Fitur keamanan yang kuat dan antarmuka yang ramah pengguna telah menjadikannya solusi andalan bagi masyarakat Filipina yang mencari layanan perbankan digital yang lancar.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\";max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Kode Channel</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"648b3370-267a-47a5-bafd-0cfb81370827\">PSBANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">Mata Uang</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"89cc4585-3036-4f0a-847a-3a0f634c0a27\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block